Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, on Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the fierce battle on \NTenroujima, we somehow returned home alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to being put in suspended \Nanimation by the first master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except seven years had \Npassed while we were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened to our \Nguild why we were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems a lot happened, and \Nthere's a lot we still don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,about this world that's seven \Nyears past the one we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three months from now, the \Nmajor event that decides
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the number one guild in Fiore will be held:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:14.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a festival in which people compete \Nin various events using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During the seven years we were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail became the weakest \Nguild in the kingdom of Fiore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so to get back to number one, we decided \Nto participate in the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:30.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But those of us in the Tenrou \Ngroup have a seven-year "blank",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so we may not be able to keep up with \Nthe fighting styles of this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three months until the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're going to have a \Ntraining camp at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Song of the Stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People! We didn't come here to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell us that, dressed like {\i1}that{\0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The key is variation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Play hard, eat a lot, sleep a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving out training, the \Nmost important point of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time this training camp is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll at least be able to beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming race!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand castle building contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suntan contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we go back \Nto the inn and take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They enjoyed the hell out of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we can cut them \Nsome slack on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:53.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tanned Gray is dreamy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this word?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:09.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the other members of Fairy Tail \Nbegan their training in different areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the water pressure \Nundersea is extremely heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he can use Roar of the Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not yet. That ain't \Nenough to do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta be able to increase \Nmy power even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let myself lose to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I want to do \Nsomething about my weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,my lack of magic power stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, you need to build \Nup your spiritual strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and grow the depth\N of the container of your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the land... the wind... \Nenergy... with your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then breathe, as if you're \Nbecoming one with nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way, Lucy-sama. Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release a little more magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:06:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla-sama did the same kind of training \Nto improve her Celestial Spirit Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Have you ever heard of the "One Magic"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic at the beginning of all magic, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Hades said he wanted to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:25.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from my mother \Ntoo, but it didn't sound dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:31.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or have anything to do with Zeref \Nor some "World of Great Magic".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the One Magic that my mother \Ntalked about is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hades never could have gotten it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you can't even imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At first glance, it seems easy to \Nobtain, but it's very difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and even while it's a strong power that \Ncertainly surpasses everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's also a very weak power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother told me that all \Nmagic starts from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think "One \NMagic" is actually "love".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hades had thought the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe he wouldn't have \Nfallen to the dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Much more stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna shut up anyone who \Nlooks down on our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show 'em all \Nthe power of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The stars are so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone else \Nis training hard, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're looking up at the \Nstars right now, just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try harder, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second day of the beach training camp, \Nthree months before the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel up to scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we seriously train our bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:20.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the second day, but already \Nour magic power has risen a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the same pose as \NGray-sama... It's so moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep training like \Nthis for three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then catching up to this age \Nwon't just be a dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, all you \Njerks from other guilds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what three months of fiery \Ntraining does for Fairy Tail members!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:48.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought, "Just three \Nmonths?", but if we train efficiently,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:51.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's more like "We have three whole months?", you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! There's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:59.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to appear from there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment time, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Spirit maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, with Lucy in \Nthe Fairy Sphere for seven years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Celestial Spirits she has a contract with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,must have been in the Celestial \NSpirit World that whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! During the "Key \Nof the Starry Heavens" affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I summoned them without thinking \Nabout it, but that's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,seven years had passed before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:25.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor spirits! And it's Lucy's \Nfault... Lucy's fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's not a big problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Spirit World is \Nin danger of being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of the Celestial \NSpirit World awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to bring all of you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When a friend asks for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! As far as I know, humans can't \Nenter the Celestial Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:13.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wear Celestial Spirit clothes, you'll \Nbe able to move about the Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I'm not mentally prepared yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...left behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Celestial Spirit World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huge moustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Spirit King!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the king here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So informal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard the Celestial Spirit World \Nis in danger of destruction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,*smile*
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy and friends! Let us celebrate your \Nrelease from the shackles of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the "in danger \Nof destruction" thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mooo! You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing the blank look on Lucy-san's \Nface as we tricked her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and while she's cosplaying Celestial \NSpiritwear no less is priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we'd surprise you-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even now, if you need a haircut to look \Nnice for the party, leave it to me-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:23.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought in our own way of how to \Ncelebrate the homecoming of Lucy and all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to celebrate it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't all materialize in \Nthe human world at once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we called all of you to \Nthe Celestial Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just did it this one time, we!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is a one-time privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what this is about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it's about, \Nas it were-moshimoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised the hell out of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:53.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! You can run into my \Narms if you like, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:14:03.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then! Tonight, we shall drink in great \Nquantities! And sing! And make merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a party with my old friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too bad about the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Horologium-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. This is a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for that last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I need no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... um... it was embarrassing \Nhaving no clothes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... That was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I apologize for that," he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the woman who once shared \Na body with Lucy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shared a body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll end up like Lucy at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen any of these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give \Nyou one as a souvenir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! He's just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is \Na Celestial Spirit too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! There are tons of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many Nicolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:31.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san! Mooo! As always, \Nyou've got a nice body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you jump up and down for me a moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that Celestial Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! What is this food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crab pescatore, garnished \Nwith stardust butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's veal cutlet in succulent sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this is a strange place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:16:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know the Celestial Spirit \NWorld became like this either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of these is my Plue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, though you are my old friend, \Nthis is my first time inviting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That just goes to show how \Nmuch he means to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:40.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old friend, I can see you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old friend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:17:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the bond between us will never be broken
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:11.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in the infinite wilderness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold back tears
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and move on towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:31.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the star that's meant for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I shine bright
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This song is meant for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so show me your smile
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten anything so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:50.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure I can have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want these clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get away from this weird Plue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got a weird bond \Ngoing on over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it rough, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Aquarius-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:16.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old friend, we shall always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:24.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call on meh or any of us anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drop by the guild again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please continue to \Ntake good care of Lucy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:46.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, old friend, may you have the \Ndivine protection of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Spirits sure do love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you're all wonderful friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We had a blast, but once \Nwe get back, we better train hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We got three months to \Ncatch up to all those other guilds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And beat Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there is one thing I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flow of time is different in the \NCelestial Spirit World and the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like one year here is only a day \Nin the human world or somethin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This would be a training paradise then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:42.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day spent in the Celestial \NSpirit World equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...three months in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! We got tired of waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Magic Games \Nare just five days away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you guys trained your hearts out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.51,0:23:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! All that time we had to train...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright! If you can bring out \Nyour latent "Second Origin" ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be able to get through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it seems like it's really painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! Huh? Have you seen Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is in the middle of battling heartache.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Just Enough \NTime to Pass Each Other!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu, let's go tease Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I ain't goin! Don't come cryin' \Nto me if you get your ass kicked!
